135
00:09:04.835 --> 00:09:06.754 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
助けるだって？

136
00:09:07.463 --> 00:09:10.550 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
加代 あんたどうなのさ

137
00:09:10.675 --> 00:09:12.843 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
