138
00:09:20.059 --> 00:09:21.852 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
色ボケんなっ このガキども！

139
00:09:21.936 --> 00:09:25.481 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:82.33% 
