151
00:10:12.987 --> 00:10:14.530 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
つけてたの！？

152
00:10:15.615 --> 00:10:18.367 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
冗談に決まってるべさ

153
00:10:18.784 --> 00:10:20.578 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
