207
00:14:37.710 --> 00:14:39.253 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
（悟）ふ～ん

208
00:14:43.591 --> 00:14:44.800 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
（ユウキ）悟君

209
00:14:45.384 --> 00:14:47.219 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:87.67% 
